  <p>
    <span>You&apos;ll be grateful that you made the change (and you&apos;ll sleep better).</span>
  </p>
  <p>
    <span></span>
  </p>
  <p>
    <span>&quot;Stop feeling sorry for yourself,&quot; we are often told. And while it can be hard to avoid self-pity entirely, mentally strong people choose to exchange self-pity for&#8194;</span>
    <span fontStyle="italic" textDecoration="underline">gratitude</span>
    <span>. Whether you choose to write a few sentences in a gratitude journal, or simply take a moment to silently acknowledge all that you have, giving thanks can transform your life.</span>
  </p>
  <p>
    <span></span>
  </p>
  <p>
    <span>Here are 7 scientifically-proven benefits:</span>
  </p>
  <list listStyleType="decimal">
    <li>
      <p>
        <span fontSize="28" fontWeight="bold">Gratitude opens the door to more relationships.</span>
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>
        <span fontSize="28" fontWeight="bold">Gratitude improves physical&#8194;</span>
        <span fontSize="28" fontWeight="bold" textDecoration="underline">health</span>
        <span fontSize="28" fontWeight="bold">.</span>
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>
        <span fontSize="28" fontWeight="bold">Gratitude improves psychological health.</span>
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>
        <span fontSize="28" fontWeight="bold">Gratitude enhances&#8194;</span>
        <span fontSize="28" fontWeight="bold" textDecoration="underline">empathy&#8194;</span>
        <span fontSize="28" fontWeight="bold">and reduces aggression.</span>
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>
        <span fontSize="28" fontWeight="bold">Grateful people&#8194;</span>
        <span fontSize="28" fontWeight="bold" textDecoration="underline">sleep&#8194;</span>
        <span fontSize="28" fontWeight="bold">better.</span>
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>
        <span fontSize="28" fontWeight="bold">Gratitude improves&#8194;</span>
        <span fontSize="28" fontWeight="bold" textDecoration="underline">self-esteem</span>
        <span fontSize="28" fontWeight="bold">.</span>
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>
        <span fontSize="28" fontWeight="bold">Gratitude increases mental strength.</span>
      </p>
    </li>
  </list>
